{"tid":1781600,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚同一大班friend去打邊爐 掂到個friend個friend隻手","createTime":"2019-12-13T09:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T18:11:54.000Z","uid":205742,"like":10,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ab5f312b135873b1ea91f67ee4efdc853538f2e3","tid":1781600,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:34:11.000Z","msg":"咁事緣我哋就一大班人十幾個，咁有個女仔friend帶咗兩個唔識嘅女仔一齊嚟，一個肥婆，一個正正常常咁，本來我都好期待，話晒都有機會識下新女仔，特登洗咗個頭，落咗gel諗住溝死女啦，終於有機會出pool啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老味 兩個都唔靚嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等我仲特登洗頭用埋護髮素... 咁之後大家就坐低啦，就係兩張長枱嚟嘅，咁我個friend就坐係我隔離，佢個friend就坐係我斜對面，本來都無乜嘢，咁開始叫嘢食啦，我就問佢食唔食雞子，佢哋成班女仔居然話唔食.... 話叫我自己一個爐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁算啦唔食咪唔食囉 屌你老味臭閪呀 居然同我叫午餐肉 打邊爐午乜撚嘢餐肉呀 你哋懶係嘢咁樣話要叫清湯 但就叫午餐肉搞撚到個湯底粉撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後臨遞紙個陣，坐我斜對面果個（普通）就叫我比張紙佢睇下，一個唔覺意就摸到佢隻食指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁本身都不以為意，之後佢剔多幾碟菜就交咗單<br />\n<br />\n話咁快，啲嘢食就嚟，咁我都無理其他人，快快手落晒啲肥牛，自己jepjep聲咁食晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，突然之間，佢個普通friend就問：呢pat血淋淋嘅嘢係咩嚟架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好核突呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雞子！！！ 明明我已經搽咗，個樓面都照俾我哋 咁比咗就無謂晒啦 橫掂我又想食，我就一手由佢手上拎起咗碟雞子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知唔小心摸到佢隻白滑幼嫩手<br />\n<br />\n佢：「你做咩掂我隻手?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」 <br />\n我個反應係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後全部人靜晒 望晒過嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚇到我即刻縮手 啲雞子耷耷耷耷担咁跌晒落去個爐度<br />\n「啊！！！！！好熱呀」坐我對面個肥婆比啲雞子彈到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係柒撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以後應該唔會再同佢哋出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係你隻手真係好滑 我無心摸你的 對唔住阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果無啲咁嘅誤會我諗我應該拎咗你電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e2ea71508968acc01b1603181827065090d37f","tid":1781600,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:35:42.000Z","msg":"可唔可以俾個機會我"},{"pid":"f63c3cd1d57c03988eeeed6da59a0b6c6e71c4b8","tid":1781600,"uid":113922,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:35:44.000Z","msg":"垃圾post"},{"pid":"f803d1a2699271c292b7b8f00ce3422d6c55977a","tid":1781600,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:35:57.000Z","msg":"我唔係痴漢嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40be971f20b9c5eacb4c9b641fc0b3afb0e21762","tid":1781600,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f63c3cd1d57c03988eeeed6da59a0b6c6e71c4b8","tid":1781600,"uid":113922,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:35:44.000Z","msg":"垃圾post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:36:16.000Z","msg":"你就垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2700b575dfbff493fa5f641771f63f9d1522e30","tid":1781